"How to build the hardware?" You may ask. To rebuilt the project from
source, follow the simple 2 steps.

1. Open system.xmp using Xilinx Platform Studio
2. Click Hardware - Generate bitstream

That's it!

The bitfile locates in implementation/. You need to
export it to your Xilinx SDK project in order to download the Microblaze
program to BRAM.

For SDK instructions , please checkout /sw/embedded directory.

For simulation, just run "make sim". Please follow Xilinx iSim
documentation for more details.
